this module requires following python packages: 
webrtcvad
pyaudio
deepspeech


to get the pertained model, navigate to speech_to_text directory and then run this: 
wget -O - https://github.com/mozilla/DeepSpeech/releases/download/v0.3.0/deepspeech-0.3.0-models.tar.gz | tar xvfz -

make sure the model located in ./speech_to_test directory

to run the tests: 
cd tests
python -m unittest test_AudioStream
python -m unittest test_Speech2Text


to run the speech detection: 
 python ./AudioStream.py --model ./models/output_graph.pbmm --alphabet ./models/alphabet.txt --lm ./models/lm.binary --trie ./models/trie

and speak to microphone when it prompts: 
* recording...
* done

wait for detection to happen, have FUN.


